OL,5, International best-selling author      
OL,6, Wilbur Smith has died at his home in   
OL,7, Cape Town at the age of 88, his        
OL,8, publisher has announced.               
OL,10,FHe passed away on Saturday afternoon   
OL,11,Fwith his wife, Niso, by his side, a    
OL,12,Fstatement published on the Wilbur Smith
OL,13,FBooks website said.                    
OL,15,FSmith's 49 published books have sold   
OL,16,Fmore than 140 million copies worldwide.
OL,18,FHe gained widespread recognition       
OL,19,Ffollowing the publication of his debut 
OL,20,Fnovel When the Lion Feeds in 1964.     
